# PagerDuty

Operations Engineering owns the [Ministry of Justice PagerDuty account](https://www.pagerduty.com/).

## Single Sign-On

This access method requires that you log in with a `*@digital.justice.gov.uk` or `*@justice.gov.uk` email address. Please send a [manual request](#manual-request) if you do not possess one.

Steps:

1. Navigate to the [Ministry of Justice PagerDuty SSO Link](https://moj-digital-tools.pagerduty.com/)
2. Press "Sign In With Your Identity Provider"
3. Press "Continue with GitHub"
4. If prompted, press "Take me back home."

If you have any problems accessing PagerDuty through Single Sign-On, please do not hesitate to contact Operations Engineering.

## Manual request

Our primary contact channel is [#ask-operations-engineering](https://mojdt.slack.com/archives/C01BUKJSZD4). You can use this channel to contact the team, provide feedback on our services, or request support from the Operations Engineering Team.

You can also send email to: operations-engineering@digital.justice.gov.uk
